   <b><font color="#993300"><font size="+3">PICTORIAL GUIDE TO THE</font></font></b> 
 <br>


  <b><font color="#993300"><font size="+3">ORDERS OF TRILOBITES</font></font></b> 
 <br>


 <font size="-1">last revised 06 January 2007 by <a href="mailto:smgon@aloha.net">S. M. Gon III</a></font><br>


 
